baku: Her assignment letter said "transferred."
baku: I've been around long enough to know what that word usually means.
baku: But that's her story to tell.
baku: What I know\: she arrived with a backpack too heavy for its contents —
baku: — a hat too big for her head —
baku: — and the expression of someone who made a decision and isn't sure yet if it was the right one.
